    <h2>How to Create a Simple HTML Page</h2>

    <ol>
        <li>Open a text editor (Notepad, VS Code, etc.).</li>
        <li>Create a new file and save it with a .html extension.</li>
        <li>Write the basic HTML structure.</li>
        <li>Add headings, paragraphs, and images.</li>
        <li>Save the file and open it in a web browser.</li>
    </ol>

